These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, taxi, motorbike, boat, train
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, board-games, card-games, cooking, gardening, hiking, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
 4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
15. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
16. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
17. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
18. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Transport    | train    | motorbike  | boat       | bike | airplane | car | taxi        |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | card-games | baking    | writing   | cooking   | board-games |

