.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, tea, water
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, sunflower, daisy, balloon-flower, lily, orchid
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 3. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 5. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 6. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
10. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growslily##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
15. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsrose##1
16. the person who growsrose is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta    | almond-milk | tea     | mirinda | hot-chocolate | water     | iced-tea |
| Flower       | orchid | lily      | sunflower | balloon-flower  | rose      | iris | daisy   |

