.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, skydiving, writing
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, german, chinese, indonesian, mexican, thai, australian
 1. the german is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 3. the mexican is between the chinese and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the german##1
 5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 6. the german is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 8. the german is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
10. the chinese is the chinese##1
11. the australian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
12. the thai is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
14. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |       3       |     4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
