.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, mystery, satire, spy, time-travel, western
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, may, june, september, january, october, august
 1. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching drama movies##2
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
14. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
15. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |   5    |   6    |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western    | satire | mystery | comedy | spy    | drama |
| Birthday           | august       | may | july   | june    | october    | january | september |

